				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm all for knights getting a *mini* defensive, honestly I think they would be happy if they just got to type the thing in / hotkey it.
<br />

<br />
Even a defensive for SK's / Pal's as described here that only works if you use a shield, AND cripples the shit out of your DPS, would make a paladin or a SK a viable tank for some of the ikkinz trials without some ridiculous healing.
<br />

<br />
Yes, currently a paladin could comfortably tank most stuff in the ikkinz group trials with 3 clerics, or if he and the clerics are all very well equipped, 2 clerics.
<br />

<br />
Warriors are the only *realistic* and *safe* option at the moment however.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=339789" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/vicour1/AnduranSig.jpg" border="0" /></a>
